OL,3,CAndy Burnham wins Makerfield by-
OL,4,Celection to set up challenge to Keir
OL,5,CStarmer
OL,7,FAndy Burnham has secured his return to
OL,8,Fthe House of Commons as his allies
OL,9,Fcalled on Sir Keir Starmer to hand
OL,10,Fover power.
OL,12,FThe Greater Manchester mayor won the
OL,13,FMakerfield by-election by 9,231 votes,
OL,14,Fseeing off the challenge from Nigel
OL,15,FFarage's Reform UK.
OL,17,FMr Burnham's victory sets up a
OL,18,Fpotential leadership contest unless
OL,19,Fthe Prime Minister agrees to step down.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
