OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781837270
OL,3,CAndy Burnham wins Makerfield by-
OL,4,Celection to set up challenge to Keir
OL,5,CStarmer
OL,7,FIn his victory speech he said Labour
OL,8,Fhad a "final chance to change" and "we
OL,9,Fmust act upon it".
OL,11,FSir Keir has insisted he will fight
OL,12,Fany attempt to challenge him and has
OL,13,Fbeen building up a war chest for a
OL,14,Fleadership campaign.
OL,16,FBut Mr Burnham's supporters urged the
OL,17,FPrime Minister to set out an "orderly
OL,18,Fand managed transition" of power.
OL,26,@pD@GOUpD@^O]pD@dOUqD@QO]yD@^OUzD@WO]
