OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781837270
OL,3,CAndy Burnham wins Makerfield by-
OL,4,Celection to set up challenge to Keir
OL,5,CStarmer
OL,7,FFormer cabinet minister Louise Haigh
OL,8,Fsaid she hoped Sir Keir will "do
OL,9,Fwhat's best for both the country and
OL,10,Fthe Labour Party".
OL,12,FMr Burnham increased Labour's majority
OL,13,Fin a seat which voted for Reform in
OL,14,Fcouncil elections last month.
OL,16,FFollowing his decisive victory he
OL,17,Fsaid: "Everyone knows that politics
OL,18,Fisn't working.
OL,26,@pD@^OUrD@QO]yD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/4
