OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781837270
OL,3,CAndy Burnham wins Makerfield by-
OL,4,Celection to set up challenge to Keir
OL,5,CStarmer
OL,7,F"Everyone can feel that the country
OL,8,Fisn't where it should be. Tonight
OL,9,Fcould, just could, be the turning
OL,10,Fpoint."
OL,12,FHe added: "I do say to my own party:
OL,13,Fthis is a final chance to change.
OL,15,F"This is what people said directly to
OL,16,Fme on the hundreds of doorsteps that I
OL,17,Fstood on. We must hear it, we must act
OL,18,Fupon it and we must get it right.
OL,19,FThere will be no second chance."
